e.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee106bf0750dfd3a3ffa981a33c24d5a0b6457d0","tid":2033204,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b526a4eaaf6e598de62971ddb9a92e05077d466c","tid":2033204,"uid":237358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba294abc34a68e21a760ae04322940c7a8ab14d5","tid":2033204,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:44:31.000Z","msg":"明明而家係惡安法, 樓豬仍然將重點擺咗喺惡歌法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:49:55.000Z","msg":"惡安法要反，惡歌法就唔使反?<br />\n宜家出面有527嘅討論，叫人圍立法會<br />\n我只係提供一個建議，畀諗住行動嘅人參考下<br />\n可以轉喺tg再慢慢討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"咁我都同意<br />\n圍立法會可能真係同送頭冇乜分別<br />\n但係無論有咩行動<br />\n記得惡歌法係冇引起國際關注, 惡安法先係國際重點"},{"pid":"9050be35919ba1b7dc920b9725e060e920fc87c3","tid":2033204,"uid":275160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"黎明行動 公路版<br />\n手足搭黨鐵 大量人手咁到目標地點<br />\n迫到狗車出黎 再好似今日班狗RB封隧咁<br />\n狗退就手足入場 玩到車行唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4885b1570f295aabcd5c93d9f429e7fc4ceeca","tid":2033204,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:53:32.000Z","msg":"仲有人鏈呢個選項<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日狗狗無玩2000票控好明顯係無可能告得入<br />\n上次人鏈有幾多人被捕被提告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人鏈係自發無大台嘅即興行為<br />\n所以唔係非法集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一於多條戰線分散佢老母狗力<br />\n鍾意罰抄咪由得佢抄<br />\n1000人 10000人 100000人 1000000人<br />\n抄佢老母天荒地老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九龍入元朗國出新界再去港島堅尼地城老銅灣仔柴灣直入青山<br />\n罰抄到無曬紙罰抄到手軟腳軟<br />\n<br />\n破佢老母限聚令大法就係<br />\n人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />超過8個千八萬倍<br />\n性質<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />395識7<br />\n隊形<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />守法保持2米社交距離無限延伸18區<br />\n勿做跟尾狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行得正企得正，狗狗要搜查咪由得佢原地搜查；千祈唔好做跟尾狗、狗狗刻意數人頭12345678<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陷害你就唔好睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢d惡法唔係話阻止就阻止得到<br />\n淋病老母都搞唔掂莫講話屎近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地嘅目標從來都係國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n畫面夠靚對比狗共醜陋就perfact<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda778901ed7567227368e32e94b7bcca093eca5","tid":2033204,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:55:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"745ec1016cc61a854886c4e53b78bf8f4b7828b9","tid":2033204,"uid":237358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9050be35919ba1b7dc920b9725e060e920fc87c3","tid":2033204,"uid":275160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"黎明行動 公路版<br />\n手足搭黨鐵 大量人手咁到目標地點<br />\n迫到狗車出黎 再好似今日班狗RB封隧咁<br />\n狗退就手足入場 玩到車行唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face