core":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:34:06.000Z","msg":"只需要阻止保皇黨議員去金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n怕比狗大包圍，就曠闊戰場，化爲流水，喺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各大幹道</span></span>行動<br />\n<br />\n唔要雜物路障，而係要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">夠難清理</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咩漏油撞車死火塞到啲車幾個鐘郁都郁唔到，翻工遇到一定遲硬到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔需要搞黨鐵，香港人可以繼續翻工，但係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保皇黨0票議員，人民公敵搭黨鐵，唔知會受到小市民乜嘢對待呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員屋企地址喺網上好似有得睇，可以加強針對性就更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">527一齊幫保皇黨罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:35:50.000Z","msg":"人地通宵留喺office/附近book酒店住一晚已經搞掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:43:51.000Z","msg":"你都可以早多1,2,3日<br />\n等到佢哋殺人先阻止？"}]}